description: Authentic Argentinean-style empanadas on the streets of Fort Collins are coming right to you! De Nada Empanada is baking up the best of this Argentinean treat you've ever seen! Made from homegrown and local ingredients, these great eats are sure to capture your heart from the very first bite. Try the caprese, smoked salmon, cuatro quesos, or any of the other delicious empanadas from De Nada's amazing menu today!
name: De Nada Empanada
